==古生态学==
许多兽脚类动物都是从维奥兰特农场化石遗址中发现的，包括[[瓜利乔龙|瓜利乔龙]]<ref name="apesteguia2016"/>和[[南盗龙|南盗龙]]（可能与前者代表同一种[[大盗龙类|大盗龙类]]）；[[鲨齿龙科|鲨齿龙科]]的[[牛猎龙|牛猎龙]]；<ref name="motta2016">{{Cite journal |last=Motta |first=M.J. |last2=Aranciaga Rolando |first2=A.M. |last3=Rozadilla |first3=S. |last4=Agnolín |first4=F.E. |last5=Chimento |first5=N.R. |last6=Brissón Egli |first6=F. |last7=Novas |first7=F.E. |year=2016 |title=New theropod fauna from the Upper Cretaceous (Huincul Formation) of northwestern Patagonia, Argentina |url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/304013683 |journal=New Mexico Museum of Natural History and Science Bulletin |volume=71 |pages=231–253 |via=ResearchGate}}</ref>一种[[虚骨龙类|虚骨龙类]]（由塞罗尼和同僚识别为一种[[半鸟科|半鸟科]]）和另一种未命名的鲨齿龙科，但很可能是不同的物种；以及另一种分类不明的大盗龙类。其它恐龙也包括一种[[泰坦巨龙类|泰坦巨龙类]]和一种[[鸟脚类|鸟脚类]]。维奥兰特农场的其他脊椎动物包括异齿类[[喙头目|喙头目]]的{{link-en|Patagosphenos}}；<ref name="gentil2019">{{cite journal |first=A.R. |last=Gentil |first2=F.L. |last2=Agnolin |first3=J.A. |last3=Garcia Marsà |first4=M.J. |last4=Motta |first5=F.E. |last5=Novas |year=2019 |title=Bridging the gap: sphenodont remains from the Turonian (Upper Cretaceous) of Patagonia. Palaeobiological inferences |journal=Cretaceous Research |volume=98 |pages=72–83 |doi=10.1016/j.cretres.2019.01.016}}</ref>一种[[鳄形类|鳄形类]]，可能属于[[新鳄类|新鳄类]]；一种[[有鳞目|有鳞目]]；一种[[侧颈龟亚目|侧颈龟亚目]]；和一种归类于{{link-en|鳞齿鱼|Lepidotes}}的鱼类。<ref name="motta2018"/>

